Scope
-----

This license applies to the ENTIRE repository, including but not limited to:
  - the Korean translation text and reader output (data/, dist/, docs/);
  - the translation pipeline source code (build/, Python scripts);
  - the per-chunk translation results, glossary, character data, and design docs.


